title: 11/02: Mailbag! (Recorded Fri.)  (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
We've got the latest injury news as we talk about the Colts WRs without T.Y. Hilton, expectations for Jaylen Samuels and more. Then we answer your Apple Podcast questions (9:15), your Fantasy Regulators disputes (22:40), your add/drop/trade questions (29:30) and your Start or Sit questions (40:30) at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
